spatial function name.

Handle attachments with spaces / special chars in name.
Rooted out attachment persistence errors as string/symbol problems.
Ironing out attachment/persistence issues between saves.
Correctly handle standalone attachments across document life.
Removing stub classes that were never used.
The rdoc, the rdoc, what what? the rdoc.

First pass at pagination, plus some view refactoring. Paginate by all
currently working.
Provide pre-filled hash of attachments from retrieved models.
Move to class_inheritable_accessor to prevent inheritance problems.
Use changed? to check for equality as well.
Define equality as id & _rev.  Need to check for dirty bit.
Less unexpected behavior for #save! and #create!, in line with ActiveRecord.
Only create a design doc when one doesn't already exist.
Explicitly go to 3.0.0 for ActiveSupport & Model (reject .rc)
Comply with new to_param test in ActiveModel/lint.
Added reduce and group support for views.
Added include_docs and key opts for views.

Attachments being saved, but not yet retrieved. Also, still need to
determine API for specifying attachment content type.
Reversing server/db argument order to allow localhost default.
Create a database when it doesn't yet exist.
Use cljs.tools.reader to handle namespaced maps
